{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And what she went through, I really don't know, but I suppose they took care of the people as well as they could that had survived this terrible march and had been years in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And to find her, as I say, took many years before I found her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then a call came from Chicago-- good old Chicago-- from Annamarie to tell Dr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Kempner to tell me that-- I was in Germany-- that she had seen the advertisement in Aufbau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so I got in touch with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I must say, a part of my-- I don't know whether you can say hard work or stupidity-- I just never kept up with it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I'm going to, on this trip, make an effort to see if she's still under the same telephone number.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she had married a man called Pace, P-A-C-E, who also was a survivor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, what color-- what do you look like?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What color is your hair?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she said, oh, it's red right now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I should go down to the airport in Frankfurt and tell her girlfriend that I knew her or something and so forth and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow, I neglected it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just about managed in my bureaucratic life in Germany since-- since the Nuremberg days and through all these years, until I retired.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I was busy working for Dr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Kempner.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just about managed to write to my mother as long as she lived, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I didn't get-- I had this big list of things I wanted to do, but priority is priority.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the army, who was my employer, was a very good taskmaster.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We never ran out of work, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
